summary: Item ID list done in Excel.
descriptionHtml:
A complete item ID list compiled into one Excel worksheet.  No more need to search the web or a PDF for an item code.  If you don\'t have Microsoft Office, given the simplicity of the worksheet, it should open in Microsoft Works as well with minimal changes in formatting.

Contains all in-game item names, weight, value, damage/rating, and effects/enchantments. 

The list is broken down into categories for easier use.

Took me several 8 hour days to complete this, so please endorse this file.  Thank you.

Version 1.1
- Added Spell Tomes and Powers categories.

**Disclaimer:  All information taken from the UESPWiki.
